# shellcheck source=/dev/null
# Package manager for sauzerOS
# ⚠️ NOT POSIX COMPLIANT
# GNU Coreutils and GNU tools expected
# Based on kiss package manager
#
# Simple package manager written in POSIX shell for https://kisslinux.github.io
#
